---
title: Chicken Shawarma with Chickpeas and Dukkah Courgettes
description: Shawarma is traditionally cooked on a vertical spit and grilled for a whole day. Do you have a vertical spit and a whole day? If so, go for it! If not, try this cheat's method that André has come up with. All the delicious grilled flavour with none of the faff!
